      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUSH BOODIE (1) goes very well at the course with four wins and a placing from five starts. Scored by a nose last time (18.97) in a Restricted WIN over 350m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. ZABDON COSMO (2) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only one length from Eastly Breeze in third (16.92) at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Must be included in calculations. SHE'S TIP TOP (8) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Q Lakeside over 390m behind Abode's Trilogy (22.60) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money the start prior. Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to play a prominent role. DAZZLING LIZZIE (4) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
